6901::$$$message_0062_0000_0000$$$::   I can't block them.[lr]::
6902::$$$message_0062_0000_0001$$$::Well, I can at least manage to avoid them.[lr]::
6903::$$$message_0062_0000_0002$$$::But I'm not sure I can dodge them [font italic=true]and[font italic=false] attack Shinji.::
6904::$$$message_0062_0001_0000$$$::The three sharp blades approach.[lr]::
6905::$$$message_0062_0001_0001$$$::"...Nnh, fuh!"[lr]::
6906::$$$message_0062_0001_0002$$$::I stop in my tracks, and concentrate on evading, keeping an eye on Shinji.::
6907::$$$message_0062_0002_0000$$$::I take a step to the left to dodge the blade that rushes towards my stomach.[lr]::
6908::$$$message_0062_0002_0001$$$::I twist my upper body to avoid the second blade coming towards my chest from the left after I avoid the first blade, and then I rush forward to pass the third blade flying at my unprotected forehead!::
6909::$$$message_0062_0003_0000$$$::"Not a problem. I can see where they're going!"[lr]::
6910::$$$message_0062_0003_0001$$$::Compared to Saber's attacks, this is like a game of dodgeball.::
6911::$$$message_0062_0004_0000$$$::"Tch!!! You conceited fool!"[lr]::
6912::$$$message_0062_0004_0001$$$::Three more shadows rush toward me.[lr]::
6913::$$$message_0062_0004_0002$$$::   I don't even need to see where these are going.[lr]::
6914::$$$message_0062_0004_0003$$$::The first attack showed me how far and fast these can go, so I have no trouble avoiding this attack.::
6915::$$$message_0062_0005_0000$$$::I pass through the gaps between the three overlapping shadows.[lr]::
6916::$$$message_0062_0005_0001$$$::They're no threat.[lr]::
6917::$$$message_0062_0005_0002$$$::I don't feel any danger from the shadows.[lr]::
6918::$$$message_0062_0005_0003$$$::Saber taught me that I shouldn't hesitate as long as I don't sense that the attack will be fatal.::
